              **Priority**: High
              **Estimated Effort**: 12 days`,
              labels: ['enhancement', 'phase-2', 'neural-symbolic', 'tensors', 'ggml']
            },
            {
              title: "Build Scheme/OCaml bridge for Rocq Prover dataflow",
